Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(800,1500)}本字幕由輕之國度製作 僅供試看之用\N如喜歡本作品 請支持Z版
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,1500)}片源：黑血  繁體：偉哥
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I entered high school two months ago,\NI didn't know...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.42,0:00:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The dampness of my uniform's hem,\Nsoaked by someone else's umbrella...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The smell of naphthalene,\Nclinging to someone's suit...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.76,0:00:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The warm body pushed up against my back...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.26,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The chill breeze of the air conditioner\Nagainst my face...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Shinjuku... Shinjuku station...\N- Thank you for riding with us.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I was little the sky was closer...\NSo much closer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I like the rain,\Nas with it comes the smell of the sky.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And often, on rainy mornings,\Ninstead of transferring to the subway,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I exit out the station gates.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.04,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,June
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chocolate, and... beer?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, I think I've seen her somewhere...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.94,0:03:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, my mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's fitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami no sukoshi toyomite\N(A faint clap of thunder)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,sashi kumori\N(Clouded skies)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ame mo furanu ka?\N(Perhaps rain comes)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,kimi wo todomemu\N(If so, will you stay here with me?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Garden of Words
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This morning, the JMA has declared the start of\Nthe rainy season in Kyushu,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}5 days earlier than average.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.85,0:05:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nagasaki, Saga, Kumamoto,\Nand Kagoshima prefectures{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}expect strong rains over a wide area.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought croquettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Dinner will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Ma?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky us, we get all the croquettes\Nto ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She left a letter saying not to go\Nlooking for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll be back after fighting\Nwith her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've picked out a place.\N{\i1}I'll{\i} be leaving next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that's why mom ran out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You told her yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish she could just let her children go,\Nyou know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who's making the rounds\Ndating younger men, damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? Well then I'm gonna go live\Nwith my boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's got those youthful looks, after all.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's 'cause she's never worked hard\Nher entire life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's been piling on the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You do the dishes. I've aged enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you be glad to have more space?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,'Suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me move, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, a haiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tanka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As if.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask Ma when she gets back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On sunny mornings, I transfer to the subway and\Nhead here, like I'm supposed to.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I think to myself\N“This is not what I should be doing now. ”{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:07:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.19,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No school today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And your office... Is it closed today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm skipping work again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And drinking beer in the park in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking beer alone isn't good for\Nyour health.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to eat something with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know a lot for a high school kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not me. My mom's the drinker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got snack food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You just thought to yourself\N“This woman's a freak,” didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We're human, after all.\NWe've all got our little quirks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's about time for me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Heading to school now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to only skip school\Non rainy mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe we'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, when it's raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the first day of Kanto's rainy season.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrance Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,About Tuition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A shoemaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it seems out of touch,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.53,0:11:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I enjoy creating designs and making shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm still terrible at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But despite it all,\NI want to make it my career... if I can.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.38,0:11:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never told anyone this before.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how late you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why I've called you here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Evenings, before I went to sleep...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mornings, in the moment I woke up...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized I was praying for rain.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I realized that on sunny days,\NI was in a terrible, childish place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With nothing but impatience.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.19,0:12:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She exists in a world of working adults,\Nso very far away from me...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.36,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To me she represents nothing less\Nthan the very secrets of the world.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honestly, there are only two things\NI know for sure.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One: She must think of me and my\N15 years as just some mere kid.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And two: Making shoes is the only thing\Nthat will lead me out of this place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please stay behind the yellow line\Nfor your safety.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please be careful of the closing doors.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might not come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a miracle you haven't been fired yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Is that a shoe design?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something worth showing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.71,0:14:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.76,0:14:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, sit down over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat breakfast.\NWould you like to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, but I've brought my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I cook sometimes, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's make a trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I'm not really that good a...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...cook, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a side of you I didn't expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. But it's tasty in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got... bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't patronize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have another?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.58,0:15:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Takao, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What could the three of you have gotten me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Do you think it's too late for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know what?\NI could actually taste the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So your taste disorder has improved?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.19,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But just a little while ago, all I could taste\Nwas alcohol and chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think you deciding to just quit\Nwas really for the best.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You speak to me so gently,\Nlike you're touching something fragile.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But back then, when I found it hard\Neven to breathe,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you didn't believe me. You only listened to\Nthe voices around you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:17:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then we'll start the paperwork\Nfor you leaving after the holiday.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll notify the higher-ups.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Sorry to cause you all this trouble\Neven after we split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.23,0:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad, really...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,About that old woman you met.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the one you keep talking about\Nwho brings her lunch box to the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like you've really struck a chord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since then...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.93,0:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...I've been nothing but lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's raining again today in Kanto.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here at Shinjuku Station's south exit,\Nthe commuters all have umbrellas in their hands.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,July
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always ended up\Neating your food, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you said you wanted it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This book isn't cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually making a pair of shoes right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... A pair for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided whose shoes yet...\NThey're women's shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I haven't been able to\Nget them right, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... Before I knew it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to walk properly anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... About a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know anything about her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her job, her age...\NWhat worries she carries...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.57,0:20:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even her name...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And yet I can't help but be charmed by her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.64,0:21:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The rainy season is officially over 10 days\Nlater than normal in the Kanto region.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The current temperature in the city\Nis 26 degrees.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.31,0:21:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Like someone just flicked a switch,\Nthe sunny days came one after another.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh sure, now I think to myself\N“I'm glad that he's not skipping class anymore”...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in reality...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...I wish the rainy season had never ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This park sure is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.68,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Japanese gardens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go next?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a greenhouse?\NLet's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like a totally different place\Non sunny days.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't you eat dinner with us, Takao?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.37,0:22:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got my part-time job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.21,0:22:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This late?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.63,0:22:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to impose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite! I'm going to be living with him\Nfrom now on, so just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.09,0:22:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.39,0:22:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.01,0:22:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a cute kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice his shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're handmade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just some ugly moccasins, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.90,0:22:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a bright future, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he'd make shoes for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? Teenagers' interests\Nchange on a whim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My brother moved out, and\Nthe rainless days continued.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.08,0:22:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no excuse to head to that place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}August\NAnd then, it was summer vacation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,August
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I worked part-time almost\Nevery day over the summer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, maybe chicken with cashew nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- We'll order it.\N- Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to earn what I could\Nfor tuition to a vocational school.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.70,0:23:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tools and leather cost money, too.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, I missed her, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think it's clinging to those feelings\Nthat is keeping me a little kid.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.97,0:24:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I've decided to create shoes\Nthat'll make her want to get up and walk.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What~ will the weather~ be tomorrow~?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.32,0:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not a bit smarter at the age of 27\Nthan I was at the age of 75.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.33,0:24:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always been here,\Nstuck in the same place.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.75,0:25:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,September
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like Tsukishima...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.59,0:25:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to have got that confused for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.18,0:25:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,English class is no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.02,0:25:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cause Kiso's a pushover.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.48,0:25:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Akizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.23,0:25:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, long time no see.\NLooks like you guys got a tan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.49,0:25:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we went to the beach a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.74,0:25:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still as pale as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.82,0:25:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you do over summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.07,0:25:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Worked the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.16,0:25:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.25,0:25:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lonely way to spend\Nyour high school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.42,0:25:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,School, part-time job, housework.\NSchool, part-time job, housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.92,0:25:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I skip school sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.34,0:25:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nyou are late a lot, Akizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.42,0:25:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, this guy never shows up\Nfor 1st period when it rains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.01,0:25:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a condition where I can't ride\Nthe subway on rainy mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.76,0:26:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.03,0:26:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.07,0:26:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.91,0:26:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, save it for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.03,0:26:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.95,0:26:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Same goes for the rest of you.\N- I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.12,0:26:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i} be here until after 5th period.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.70,0:26:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'd be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.29,0:26:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki came to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.47,0:26:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't hear about Yuki quittin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.47,0:26:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I didn't even know who she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.81,0:26:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have old man Takehara for lit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.65,0:26:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki was always having trouble\Nwith the 3rd year girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.82,0:27:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Miss Yukino\Ndidn't do anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.66,0:27:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's boyfriend fell for Miss Yukino,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.74,0:27:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and as payback everyone in the class\Ntreated Miss Yukino terribly.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.33,0:27:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They spread so many rumors\Neven her parents heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.50,0:27:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It went so far she couldn't\Ncome to school any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.76,0:27:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki's just too kind. She should have\Nbrought it right to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.76,0:27:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We told Mr. Ito {\i1}again{\i} and again!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.68,0:27:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't want to make trouble\Nfor the school in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.48,0:27:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those upperclassmen...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.70,0:27:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know their names?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.08,0:27:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.88,0:28:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He totally sucks at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.76,0:28:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.18,0:28:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, you sure go through 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.73,0:28:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want, frosh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.06,0:28:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the 3rd year, Aizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.40,0:28:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An admirer?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.74,0:28:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.86,0:28:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like Miss Yukino is quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.24,0:28:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.49,0:28:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care about what happens to\Nthat slutty hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.41,0:28:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does this guy think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.75,0:28:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.25,0:28:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.43,0:28:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go tell a teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.76,0:28:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Never seen this kid before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Fallen for that old hag?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creep! Does he even know\Nhow old she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.77,0:28:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy, she must have tricked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She might go for him now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.02,0:29:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she ain't a teacher no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.28,0:29:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.28,0:29:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You should thank us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.93,0:29:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm waiting for the rain.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.52,0:30:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami no sukoshi toyomite\N(A faint clap of thunder)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.86,0:30:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,furazu to mo\N(Even if rain comes not)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.53,0:30:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,warewa tomaramu\N(I will stay here)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.95,0:30:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,imoshi todomeba\N(Together with you)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.29,0:30:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the correct answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.87,0:30:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the right response to the tanka\NI told you when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.09,0:30:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it rains, I wonder if you will be staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.26,0:30:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In response to that verse, I answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.05,0:30:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it doesn't rain, I will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.22,0:30:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was in the classic Japanese\Nliterature textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.56,0:31:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.73,0:31:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.53,0:31:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would realize\NI was a classic literature teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.74,0:31:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, everyone at school knows about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.37,0:31:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're always off in your\Nown little world, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.37,0:31:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.21,0:31:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was acting like you\Nand drank too much beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I tripped and fell on the\NYamanote line platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.09,0:31:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.09,0:31:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. I got in a fight, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.43,0:32:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look... It looks like we just\Nswam across the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.58,0:34:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think this might...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.67,0:34:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...this might be...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.17,0:34:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the happiest...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.42,0:34:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...time of my life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.27,0:34:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.60,0:34:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've fallen in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.30,0:34:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Yukino... Miss Yukino, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.06,0:35:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be moving next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.27,0:35:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to my hometown in Shikoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.98,0:35:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I made the decision a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.40,0:35:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was practicing how to walk on my own,\Nthere in that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.66,0:35:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I'm barefoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.00,0:35:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.17,0:35:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to thank you for\Neverything, Akizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, thank you for lending me these clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.73,0:35:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll{\i} get changed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.44,0:35:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But yours aren't...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.05,0:36:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me... I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.77,0:36:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hospitality.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.09,0:37:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I made this lunch for myself,\Nbut I made too much.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.64,0:37:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So if you'd like...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.60,0:37:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't decided whose shoes yet...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.81,0:37:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're women's shoes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.81,0:37:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was acting like you\Nand drank too much beer{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.02,0:37:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I tripped and fell on the\NYamanote line platform.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.65,0:37:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Narukami no sukoshi toyomite\N(A faint clap of thunder){\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.65,0:37:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}furazu to mo\N(Even if rain comes not){\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.70,0:37:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}warewa tomaramu (I will stay here){\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.49,0:37:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imoshi todomeba (Together with you){\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.50,0:38:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.71,0:38:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino, please forget what I said earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.22,0:38:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong... I hate you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.77,0:38:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since we first met, you struck me...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.15,0:38:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...like a person I should avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.03,0:38:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Drinking beer in the morning,\Nspouting off some random tanka at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.99,0:38:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You listen all day to other people talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,yet never say a peep about yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew I was a student, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.70,0:38:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.79,0:39:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'd known you were a teacher,\NI would have never told you about the shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.21,0:39:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you think\NI'll never amount to anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.09,0:39:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So why didn't you say anything to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.64,0:39:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought maybe you'd humor\Nthe little kid's fantasies for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.72,0:39:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me I'll never live up\Nto my expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.23,0:39:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me I'll never measure up to my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.98,0:39:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew from the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.90,0:39:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, god damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.90,0:39:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me I'm in your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me that little kids should\Nrun along to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.65,0:39:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me that you hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.28,0:39:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.99,0:39:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you act like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.16,0:39:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You never say what's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.41,0:39:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You pretend it's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.50,0:39:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been living your whole life, alone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.39,0:39:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.85,0:40:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning I put on my suit\Nto go to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.27,0:40:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was... scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.11,0:40:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.95,0:40:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.78,0:40:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.87,0:40:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You... saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.46,0:40:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lived on with feelings frozen,\Nnever expressed in words,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.13,0:40:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I clumsily held you in my\Narms on a rainy night{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.31,0:40:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Street flyers and broken lamps,\Neverybody was rushing back{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.24,0:41:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not you but me who is to blame.\NI couldn't hide my own impulsiveness{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.21,0:41:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady, you started running through\Na deserted station{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.68,0:41:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unconcerned about getting soaked\Nfrom the pouring rain{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.85,0:41:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sight of you splashing through\Npuddles disappears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.02,0:41:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning comes quicker in the back alleys,\Nso I have to get hold of you now{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.36,0:41:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To say, Don't go away, don't go away{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.03,0:41:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer ended, and it came time to\Nswitch to our winter uniforms...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.87,0:41:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got terrible marks on my final exams...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.87,0:41:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasted who knows how many\Npieces of expensive leather...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.04,0:41:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I worked part-time over winter break as well...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.71,0:41:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And every time I added a layer\Nto my clothing,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.55,0:41:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wondered to myself...\Nhow was she doing?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.38,0:41:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have enough strength anymore{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.72,0:42:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voice:{\i} Miyu {\i1}lrino{\i} / Kana Hanazawa {\i1}To grab on\Nto the sky that's welled up with tears{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Voice:\NMiyu lrino {\i1}/{\i} Kana Hanazawa
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.86,0:42:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are strong enough not to feel hurt\Nbecause of my unchanging heart{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.24,0:42:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Original Story/Screenplay: Makoto Shinkai Lady. All wet\Nfrom the rain, you looked into my eyes for a moment{\i}
