Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.09,0:42:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Background Art Director Hiroshi\NTakiguchi Whistling, I {\i1}walk{\i} after {\i1}you{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.26,0:42:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have known you too much, just like\Nthe night when we first quarreled,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.43,0:42:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To say, Don't go away, don't go away{\i}
