Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.70,0:45:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This letter has gotten quite long\Nwithout me even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.62,0:45:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for reading it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.24,0:45:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you are doing well, Akizuki.\NI wish the warm days of Spring come soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.29,0:45:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yukari Yukino
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.42,0:45:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was practicing how to walk, too.\NI think that now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.10,0:45:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One day, when I can walk\Nmuch farther on my own...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.35,0:45:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I will go see her.{\i}
